{
  "stem": "2539.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in Lutsk, in the ghetto--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in the ghetto-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a third room in which lived some tradesmen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't exactly know what tradesmen they were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was a family with two or three sons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we all shared the same kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I understand from people who survived, that just before they liquidated the ghetto in Lutsk, they wanted gifted tradesmen to keep them longer alive, so that they can benefit; so they-- the tradesmen can do jobs for the Germans and for the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I understand that my sister found myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I suspect that one of these tradesman's sons took her along with him to that castle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remember that medieval castle had a courtyard in the middle?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where they took the tradesmen to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody told me that Lola was seen in that castle, still alive with the tradesmen, but not-- but they liquidated them all right there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know when.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't know whether she was killed in between the 22nd and the 25th of August like the rest of the ghetto, or whether she was killed a few weeks later.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I suspect that because the tradesmen were there, sharing that kitchen, the apartment-- a beautiful family-- beautiful family-- the mother was such a darling woman.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Look.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Honestly, I mean, we-- you see, I suspect that my sister went with one of these boys who was chosen as a good tradesman, to go to the castle.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she probably went along with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
